\c 63
\s Dhavhidhi unoshuva Jehovha
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi, panguva yokugara kwake parenje raJudha.
\p
\v 1 Mwari, imi muri Mwari wangu; ndichakutsvakai mangwanani; Mweya wangu unenyota kwamuri, nyama yangu inokushuvai, Panyika yakaoma, inonzwisa nyota, isina mvura.
\v 2 Naizvozvo ndakatarira kwamuri panzvimbo tsvene, Kuti ndione simba renyu nokubwinya kwenyu.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti unyoro hwenyu hunokunda upenyu;
\s Miromo yangu ichakurumbidzai.
\p
\v 4 Naizvozvo ndichakuvongai ndichiri mupenyu;
\s Ndichasimudza maoko angu nezita renyu.
\p
\v 5 Mweya wangu uchaguta
\s nezvinenge mwongo namafuta;
\s Muromo wangu uchakurumbidzai nemiromo inofara kwazvo;
\p
\v 6 Kana ndichikurangarirai panhoo yangu,
\p Ndichikufungai panguva dzousiku.
\v 7 Nokuti makanga muri mubatsiri wangu,
\s Pamumvuri wamapapiro enyu ndipo pandichafara kwazvo.
\p
\v 8 Mweya wangu unokunamatirai nesimba rose;
\s Ruoko rwenyu rworudyi runonditsigira.
\p
\v 9 Asi avo, vanotsvaka kuparadza mweya wangu,
\s Vachapinda munzvimbo dzapasi dzenyika.
\p
\v 1 Â° Vachaiswa pasimba romunondo;
\s Vachava mugove wamakava.
\p
\v 11 Asi mambo achafara munaMwari;
\s Mumwe nomumwe anopika naye
\s achafara kwazvo;
\s Nokuti muromo wavanoreva nhema uchadzivirwa.
